query:
INSERT INTO pull_requests (repo_id, number, author_id, created_at, merged_at, executed, score)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
        ON CONFLICT (repo_id, number) DO UPDATE
        SET 
            merged_at = EXCLUDED.merged_at,
            executed = EXCLUDED.executed
        RETURNING id
